    <text>
        <body>
        	<div1 type="letter">
        		<pb entity="DSSR_000001107_0149"/>
        		<head>Jim to Mon. Paul A. Rockwell <date value="1916-05-09">May 9th ‘16</date></head>
        		
        		<opener>
            <dateline><date value="1916-05-09">May 9th ‘16</date></dateline>
            
            <salute>Dear Paul:</salute>
        		</opener>
        		
            <p>
            Thanks for your
            note re the candy.  The
            ordinary packages sent to
            soldiers land out here O.K.
            That is we have all the
            facilities known to the war
            and the candy would arrive
            by any method you used.
            Keep a couple of tins for
            yourself; and send me
            a note as to amount of
            duty and other expense.  Sorry
            you have been bothered with
            it.  Its damn nice of you
            
            <pb entity="DSSR_000001107_0151" n="[p.2]"/>
            
            to take the trouble.
            </p><p>
            All of our machines
            are here now and work
            is well under way.
            Its pleasant to have one’s
            own aeroplane [sic] and a crew
            to boss.  I was worried
            for I’d never flown a 
            Baby, but got away  with
            it all right.
            </p><p>
            Cowden is still on 
            permission and Prince
            went in to get his
            machine at Le Bourget.
            </p><p>
            I’ve sent Mowrer 3
            screeds and no word 
            from him.
            
            <pb entity="DSSR_000001107_0150" n="[p.3]"/>
            
            Kiffin tells me you’re 
            coming out.  Good!
            Hurry up old pal.
            Will be mighty glad to
            see you.  We’ve a room
            in our house you can
            take unless someone grabs
            it before.
            </p>
        		
        		<closer>
            <salute>Must get to bed
            now.
            
            My best
            </salute>
            
            <signed>Mac.</signed>
            
            <seg type="postscript">
            Don’t bother about candy
            if its any trouble &mdash; eat
            it.
            </seg>
        		</closer>
        		
        		<pb entity="DSSR_000001107_0152"/>
        		
            <!-- [The envelope is addressed to Mon. Paul A. Rockwell, Roosevelt Hotel, 63 Ave d’ Jena, Paris.] -->
            
            <pb entity="DSSR_000001107_0153"/>
